modules.description: Processes CGI environment variables and query parameters, extracting and decoding key-value pairs from HTTP requests. Handles URL-encoded strings and parses form data submitted via GET or POST methods. Enables retrieval of user input for web application logic.

Provides functions to parse CGI arguments and cookies, read request bodies, handle multipart data, and generate HTTP headers. Works with strings, lists of key-value pairs, and a field_data record for multipart content. Used to extract query parameters, process form data, and construct responses in web applications.
